products.description:
E&C KS-3 Ultra+ AEG Gel Blaster Replica

The E&C KS-3 Gel Blaster delivers a compact CQB-focused platform with outstanding realism and modern performance. Inspired by the KS military rifle platform, it features a full metal external build paired with an Ultra+ gearbox, combining a brushless motor system, bluetooth Mosfet, Carbon steel gears, and reinforced internals for serious players and collectors alike.

KS-3 rifle was originally developed by Knight’s Armament Company.

The KS-1 was adopted by the British military under the service designation L403A1 and is currently in service with the UK Royal Marines. The KS-3 is the CQB-focused variant, used by South Korean military units.

• Full metal construction for realistic weight and durability

Design Background (For Reference Only): Difference Between G17 and G45

The following information refers exclusively to real firearm models and is provided for general background context only. It does not describe the specifications or performance of this toy/gel blaster product.

In real firearm, the Glock 17 and Glock 45 differ mainly in slide and frame configuration. While the Glock 17 features a full-size slide and frame, the Glock 45 combines a compact slide (from the Glock 19) with a full-size grip—offering a “crossover” design for improved handling and faster draw.

products.description:
• Capacity: 1,000 ml

  • Weight: 510g

  • Pressure Rating: Equivalent ~19 kg / ~270 PSI at 20 °C (at temperature above 20 °C, we seriously suggest using a lower pressure gas, as this stuff is full-throttle)

  • Formula Type: Secret-formula high performance gas

  • Additives: Lubrication oil + performance agents (manufacturer spec)

  • Certification: DOT certified bottle (as per BeistOutdoor Airsoft Gas range)

  • Use Case: Gel blaster GBB pistols / rifles requiring high-pressure gas (Not suitable for use in temperature above 20 °C)

  • Storage / Safety: Store in cool, dry area; avoid direct sunlight and puncture risk
Please Note: 19kg Gas is consider a VERY high working pressure, which will make it too powerful for some GBB Pistols. Not recommended for use in Glock style pistols, and this gas should only be used in the coldest winter months.

NOTE: DUE TO BEING A FLAMMABLE MATERIAL WE CAN NOT SHIP THIS EXPRESS BY AIR, IF YOU CHOOSE EXPRESS WE WILL STILL SEND IT STANDARD SHIPPING.

products.description:
E&C COLT M4A1 RIS AEG Gel Blaster| E&C Ultra Line:
E&C COLT M4A1 RIS delivers unmatched authenticity and performance. With its 1:1 M4 RIS replica design for true realism on the outside, and a reinforced gearbox with a programmable ETU MOSFET on the inside, this blaster combines durability, precision, and cutting-edge tech.

Exterior Features:

• Authentic full marking

• 5-point adjustable stock

• Compact body with a long barrel

• Classic M4 detachable carry handle

• Equipped with a sling mount – making it easy to carry

• Quad rail handguard – allows for greater compatibility with a wide range of accessories

Interior Features:

• Reinforced CNC Gearbox – Durable steer gears, Full steel teeth piston, CNC copper high-durability cylinder head, CNC 7075 alluminum alloy piston head, stainless steel cylinder, CNC 7075 aluminum alloy / Copper nozzle, CNC aluminum alloy bearing shaft motor, Programmable electronic trigger unit mosfet

• Mosfet: Programmable ESHOOTER v2 basic mosfet (unable to connect to eshooter app)

•AEG-Powered: Equipped with an Automatic Electric Gun (AEG) system, providing reliable power and consistent firing rates for superior battlefield control

Specifications:

• Length: See Picture

• Weight: 2.6 kg

• FPS: 300-320

• Outer Barrel Thread Direction: 14mm Counter Clockwise

• Materials: All parts are metal/Alloy, except for the nylon handgrip and buttstock

• Fire Modes: Safe / Semi-Auto / 3-Burst  / Full Auto

• Bolt Release: A functional bolt release that disengages the bolt after the charging handle has been pulled, locking the bolt in the drawn-back position

• Connector: T deans

• Package Includes: Gel Blaster, E&C Metal M4 Magazine, A pack of Gel Balls

Please Note: The battery and charger are sold separately.

Bosli-po 11.1V 1100mAh T Deans Battery- $31

X force Battery Balance Charger- $55

products.name: Eshooter Kestrel V3 BASIC Mosfet For Gel Blaster
products.short_description: The Kestrel V3 BASIC offers a cost-effective solution for upgrading your AEG with a dependable ETU. Switch easily from AK to G36 selector, set your desired Pre-Cocking level and access various SEMI & AUTO functions through programming.
products.description:
The Eshooter Kestrel V3 Basic Mosfet offers advanced programming options for gel blasters, including pre-cocking, semi-auto, full-auto and burst modes. Its self-learning function adjusts performance to different speeds and loads for enhanced reliability.

To ensure proper installation and maintain warranty coverage, we strongly recommend having the MOSFET installed by our qualified technicians. Any damage resulting from unauthorized installation will void the warranty.

Eshooter Kestrel V3 Basic Mosfet

  • 5 Pre-Cocking Level
    5 Pre-cocking levels and automatically determine the position of pre-cocking stop based on different speeds and loads.
  • Brushless Motor
    Support brushless and high-speed/high-torque motors.
  • Locked Rotor Protection
    When gear and motor work out of order prevents gearbox damage.
  • Active Braking
    Adaptive function to avoid gear instability, ensure piston stops in front position, increase gearbox and inside parts’ service life.
  • Support Different Batteries
    We support no matter LiPo, LiFe and LiHv batteries, working without any issue.

products.name: Eshooter Flare Smoky BT: Gel Blaster Tracer Unit
products.short_description: The Eshooter Smoky Tracer Unit designed and produced based on the feedback from gelsofters. -Oil leakage? No. -Short circuit? No. -Battery death easily? No. -BUT! Chrono? Yes! -Flame color options? Yes! -App control? Yes! -OTA avaliable? Absolutely!
products.description:
Eshooter Smoky Tracer Unit delivers ultra-realistic smoke and tracer effects, enhancing your gel blaster experience like never before.

FEATURES

  • 8 Mode Options: Muzzle Flash, Tracer with Muzzle Flash, Tracer Mode, Tracer Ratio, and each above with Smoke Mode.
  • Lightweight & Size: 105g & 126(L) x 38(φ)mm.
  • Ultra-long Standby Time: More than 3 months standy by after charging full, around 6 hours working time.
  • Wide Range of Applications: Compatible with standard, red/green tracer BBs and Gel Balls.
  • Fast response: Supports up to 50+RPS(built-in sensor can achieve higher refresh rate and faster data transmission speed).
  • Wake up by shaking: Built-in vibration sensor, automatic sleep in 5 minutes, shake the product to wake up. And you can turn off this function by app setting if you don’t need it.

ESSENTIAL OIL DISCLAIMER

  • Only use the officially provided essential oils from ESHOOTER. These exclusive oils have been certified non-toxic and harmless through MSDS testing.
  • The oil tank is manufactured from corrosion-resistant PCTG material and is intended solely for use with ESHOOTER’s certified essential oils.
  • We shall not be held liable for any product damage, personal injury, or legal consequences resulting from the use of e-cigarette oils or any other liquids from unauthorized or unknown sources.

To enjoy the full smoke effect of your Eshooter Smoky Tracer Unit, don’t forget to grab the official replacement oil for optimal performance.

products.description:
The SOLINK V5 51000RPM Brushless Long Axis Motor is the only motor on the market that allows precise speed adjustment in 1,000 RPM increments, giving you full control over performance. With an impressive operating range from 1,000 to 46,000 RPM, it’s built to suit everything from low-speed precision builds to high-speed competitive setups.

    With one-way bearing design, anti-release latch is no longer required in the gearbox. Get rid of the noise from the anti-release latch, gears turns smoother than ever in the gearbox.
  • PROGRAMMABLE
    Programming RPM and level of Torque. Customise the motor for your upgrade needs, up to 51000 rpm.
  • CNC ONE PIECE DESIGN OF SHAFT AND FRAME
    The single piece CNC frame and shaft provides a stronger base to immensely extend the lifespan of the motor.
  • Faster start, less heat emitted, faster active break, lower energy consumption.

Specification:

  • High temperature resistant quality copper windings
  • High Torque
  • High Precision CNC design
  • Material: Aluminium high quality casing

Welcome to the Cyber Custom pre-built MG STRIKE INDUSTRIES “Sentinel” DSG (dual sector gear). This AEG is set up for players that want ultimate performance. The might dsg prebuilts can only be found at Cyber Trigger. No other shop in Australia produces prebuilt DSG’S. This blaster is also sporting the optac barrel with integrated hop up meaning you maintain the aesthetics of the replica but the benefit of a hop up.This blaster will exceed expectations and turns heads every time you Brrrrrrt. We know this because all of our Cyber Custom range go through a stringent QC test and final inspection after stress testing. You can see part of this process on our youtube channel cyber trigger australia and also check out this exact blaster being fired and tested. This particular blaster was built to leave no stone unturned for unmatched performance. All our gel blasters feel amazing being fully metal exterior making them true replicas!

Shooting 290 FPS at 55 RPS!

 

SAVE $100 on this custom compared to buying the gel blaster separately with all of our prebuilt range!

 

Internally the parts list in this Cyber Custom is as follows:

*Solink brushless motor 35k

*SHS 9:1 Carbon Steel Gears

*V2 Optical bluetooth Leviathan (connects via phone app)

*Stainless steel bushings

*PA66 piston body with full metal rack and CNC 7075 Piston head

*Stainless steel ported cylinder

*Tappetless cylinder head

*SHS M150 Compression spring

*7.5mm optac barrel

*Metal E&C anti reverse latch

290 FPS (feet per second)

55 RPS (rounds per second)

Please note it is recommended to use high quality gels and high quality batteries with this high performance gel blaster to ensure the best results possible. Time to level up your gameplay today and Feel The Difference!

products.description:
Welcome to the Cyber Custom pre-built SIG MCX Virtus. This AEG is set up for players that want performance and reliability. Not only will this blaster exceed expectations but will also run game after game, we know this because all of our Cyber Custom range go through a stringent QC test and final inspection after stress testing. You can see part of this process on our youtube channel cyber trigger australia and also check out this exact blaster being fired and tested. This particular blaster was built to leave no stone unturned for unmatched performance. All our gel blasters feel amazing being fully metal exterior making them true replicas!

Shooting 330 FPS at 28 RPS!

 

SAVE $100 on this custom compared to buying the gel blaster separately with all of our prebuilt range!

 

Internally the parts list in this Cyber Custom is as follows:

*Solink brushless motor 28k

*SHS 12:1 Carbon Steel Gears

*E-shooter basic v2 mosfet (semi, auto, safe, binary, burst, pre-cock, active break & lipo protection)

*Stainless steel bushings

*PA66 piston body with full metal rack and CNC 7075 Piston head

*Stainless steel ported cylinder

*Alloy cylinder head CNC 7075 with double o-ring and sorbothane pad for correct AOE (angle of engagement)

*Alloy 7074 CNC V2 nozzle with o-ring

*PA66 tappet plate

*Stainless steel return spring

*SHS M110 Compression spring

*7.4mm alloy barrel

*Metal E&C anti reverse latch

330 FPS (feet per second)

28 RPS (rounds per second)

Please note it is recommended to use high quality gels and high quality batteries with this high performance gel blaster to ensure the best results possible. Time to level up your gameplay today and Feel The Difference!

products.description:
Eshooter V2 SE Mosfet is a budget-friendly Bluetooth MOSFET that delivers essential performance and smart control.

Key Features of the Eshooter Kestrel Bluetooth Mosfet/ ETU System

•Pre-Cocking Adjustment
Fine-tune pre-cocking mode with 100 levels of precision, ensuring optimal performance in all firing modes and improving trigger response.

•Brushless Motor Support
Fully compatible with high-speed, high-torque, and brushless motors for enhanced power and reliability.

•Selector Modes
Customize firing modes, including SAFE, SEMI, BINARY, Burst, AUTO, and Sniper, for a tailored shooting experience that suits your tactical needs. (AUG Mode is not available)

•Personalized Settings
Save up to 5 custom settings and rename your device for a truly personalized experience. Switch profiles effortlessly via the app.

•ROF Control (Rate of Fire)
Adjust the rate of fire to your preference, even when using high-voltage batteries, for consistent and controlled performance.

•Sensor Calibration
Built-in calibration ensures precise alignment with your gearbox for optimal performance and accuracy.

•Battery Protection
Prevents over-discharge of LiPo/LiFe batteries by monitoring voltage levels. The app provides low-battery warnings to ensure your equipment stays powered.

•Active Brake
Prevents double shots by ensuring the piston stops in the forward position, extending the life of internal components and improving reliability.

•Cycle Detection
Detects gear cycle completion with a rack sensor. Supports DSG, HSG, and standard gear configurations for versatility.

•Firmware Updates
Keep your system up to date with free OTA (Over-The-Air) updates via the Eshooter App.

•Smart Fuse Protection
Built-in intelligent fuse system protects the motor, battery, and controller from overheating, overloading, and short circuits.

•Sleep Mode
Automatically enters sleep mode after one hour of inactivity to conserve battery power. Simply reconnect the battery to reactivate. Perfect for long MILSIM games.

•Locked Rotor Protection
Safeguards your gearbox from damage when gears or motors encounter issues.

•Sniper Delay Mode
Adds realistic shot delays of 0.5s, 1s, 2s, or 3s for precision shooting and a more immersive experience.

products.description:
E&C COLT M4A1 Gel Blaster| E&C Value Line：

This is E&C’s latest Value Line product — one of the few gel blasters on the market that combines high performance, durability, and budget-friendliness.

Weighing just 2.2 kg, this blaster is 0.8 kg lighter than typical full-metal models, yet it retains all the exterior details and shooting performance of a full-metal blaster. The only change is the receiver, which is made of nylon.

Despite this, the price is only half that of a full-metal blaster! Truly delivering more value without compromising quality.

E&C COLT M4A1 Gel Blaster — An upgraded entry-level blaster featuring a metal handguard, durable nylon receiver, and a metal-reinforced gearbox. Reliable performance with a solid build, perfect for beginners stepping into the game.

  • Reinforced Nylon Receiver

  • Iron sight
  • Reinforced Nylon Grip
  • Reinforced Nylon Stock
  • Weight: 2.2KG
  • Plug: Tamiya
  • FPS: ~ 345 Feet Per Sec
  • Outer Barrel Thread Direction: 14mm Counter Clockwise
  • Bolt Release: Functional bolt release, that releases the bolt after the charging handle has been pulled, which locks the bolt in the drawn back position
  • Buttstock: Retractable buttstock
  • Fire Modes: Semi/Full-Auto, Safety

  • Materials: Metal alloy, polymer polymer

products.name: SOLINK Digital Programming Board For Solink V5 Motor
products.short_description: SOLINK Digital Programming Board allows precise speed adjustments, offering customizable settings for enhanced performance and control in your gel blaster.
products.description:
SOLINK Digital Programming Board Setup Guideline:

• Motor speed can be adjusted between 10k-46k rpm with 1k rpm increments with this digital programming card (Default value: 46k rpm ,11.1v)Please Note: Digital programming board  only work with V5 Brushless motor (Click here to see more), not workable for our other models either other brands motor.
• The starting torque of the motor can be adjusted by current change. (Default value:60%)
• It can also be used to check the health of the battery, and automatically detects the battery voltage and percentage of remaining charge after the battery is linked

Button Description:

• M Button: Short press to select the item to be set, long press to quickly reconnect when disconnected from the motor.

• –  Button: Short press to decrease the value of the selected item, long press to quickly decrease the value of the selected item.

• + Button: Short press to increase the value of the selected item, long press to quickly increase the value of the selected item.

• S Button: Long press to save the settings to the motor.

Attention:

1) Some malfunctions, poor contact, or unexpected situations may cause the motor to rotate unexpectedly. Therefore, the motor must be securely fixed before using this product.

2) The motor must be reliably connected to the cable of the board before the board can be powered on, otherwise it may cause accidental rotation of the motor.

3) The battery voltage used to power the programming board must be higher than 7.4V, otherwise it may cause the motor to rotate unexpectedly.

4) After the settings are saved, the programming board will self-disconnect and disconnect from the motor. If you want to reset it, you must power it on again or press and hold the M button to reconnect.

5) While in the setting menu, do not disconnect the motor wires, otherwise it may cause the motor to rotate unexpectedly.

6) If the maximum current rating of the ETU is lower than the defined starting current of the motor,we are NOT responsible for the damage it might caused.

7) Please confirm the correct polarity before installation. Do not reverse the positive and negative connections. Damage caused by incorrect polarity is not covered under warranty.

products.name: AEG Gearbox Retuning & Optimization Service
products.description:
CyberTrigger’s expert service team provides professional gearbox retuning and optimization, ensuring your blaster functions smoothly, reliably, and efficiently straight out of the box. Many stock blasters are always not in the best condition due to quality control issues or factory assembly inconsistencies, resulting in suboptimal performance, inefficient or premature wear.

Our retuning service involves a full disassembly and reassembly of your gearbox with precision adjustments, enhancing durability, FPS consistency, and overall performance.

Service Includes:

✔ Gear Reshimming – Ensures perfect meshing between gear teeth, producing a crisp operation sound and significantly increasing gear longevity.

✔ Bushing & Bearing Locking – Securely fastens bushings and bearings using high-strength retaining compounds, preventing movement and ensuring stable gear meshing.

✔ Gearbox Radiusing – Strengthens the gearbox shell, dramatically reducing the risk of cracks and structural failures.

✔ Sorbothane Cylinder Head Padding – Adds a high-quality Sorbothane pad to the back of the cylinder head to absorb piston impact and reduce gearbox stress.

✔ Angle of Engagement Correction – Optimizes piston engagement via Sorbothane padding, increasing piston lifespan and reducing wear.

✔ Gear Screw Locking – Applies Loctite to sector gear and pinion gear screws to prevent loosening during operation.

✔ Pinion-to-Bevel Alignment – Fine-tunes the alignment between the pinion gear and bevel gear, preventing stripping or gear damage.

✔ Motor Base Plate Locking – Secures the motor base plate to prevent unwanted adjustments, avoiding catastrophic damage to the pinion and bevel gears.

✔ Regreasing of Gears & Airseal Components – Improves compression, enhancing FPS stability and consistency.

✔ Piston O-Ring Upgrade – Replaces the stock O-ring with a high-quality variant, ensuring better compression, range, and FPS consistency.

Service Benefits:

CyberTrigger’s retuning process ensures that every aspect of your blaster’s gearbox is professionally optimized for performance, durability, and reliability.

All services are performed by expert technicians, and the retuned gearbox comes with a extended 3-month warranty, providing you with peace of mind and a superior gaming experience.

products.name: E&C G18C Semi/Full Auto GBB Pistol Gel Blaster Replica
products.short_description: The G18C GBB Pistol Gel Blaster offers realistic semi/full-auto firing, durable construction, and accurate performance for an exciting gameplay experience.
products.description:
The Glock 18C Gas Blowback Pistol Gel Blaster combines realism and performance for an exhilarating shooting experience. This replica mirrors the real-steel version, offering both semi-automatic and full-auto firing modes, ensuring versatility and excitement in every skirmish.

  • Exceptional Performance
    Equipped with gas blowback technology, the Glock 18C delivers rapid-fire action and realistic recoil, enhancing the authenticity of gameplay. Crafted with precision and attention to detail, this gel blaster guarantees an immersive shooting experience. Players will enjoy powerful and accurate performance, making it perfect for competitive battles and target practice.
  • Durable Design
    Constructed from high-quality materials, the Glock 18C withstands the rigors of intense use. Its durable construction ensures reliability and longevity, allowing you to engage in countless skirmishes without compromising performance. The sleek black finish not only looks stylish but also adds to the overall appeal of the pistol.
  • User-Friendly Features
    The Glock 18C GBB Pistol features an intuitive design that caters to both seasoned players and newcomers. Its simple loading and shooting mechanisms make it easy to use, while straightforward maintenance keeps it in top condition.

Whether you’re an experienced gel blaster or trying it for the first time, the Glock 18C GBB Pistol Gel Blaster is the perfect choice. Dive into thrilling gel blasting adventures and enjoy the excitement this impressive replica offers!
